{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879822400,"sessionID":"ses_28550e39affe44ngNC3XoJfwct","part":{"id":"prt_d7aaf9818001IjjcWqPMvjlSFq","messageID":"msg_d7aaf8842001guUmSp88l7FBED","sessionID":"ses_28550e39affe44ngNC3XoJfwct","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_69d23385316241f5a4f44fd8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-037: PCAP 分析器示例应用 - Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PCAP analyzer example application in the AgentCube `example` module.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-037\n10: - **Module**: `example`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Reference Sources**: \n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Files to Add\n18: \n19: | Path | Description | Type |\n20: |------|-------------|------|\n21: | | | |\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## Files to Modify\n26: \n27: | Path | Description | Change Type |\n28: |------|-------------|-------------|\n29: | | | |\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## Files to Delete\n34: \n35: | Path | Description |\n36: |------|-------------|\n37: | | |\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## Requirements\n42: \n43: ### AR-037-001: \n44: \n45: The system SHALL \n46: \n47: #### Scenario: AR-037-001-A — \n48: \n49: - **GIVEN** \n50: - **WHEN** \n51: - **THEN** \n52: \n53: ---\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-037: PCAP 分析器示例应用 - Delta Specification\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PCAP analyzer example application in the AgentCube `example` module.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-037\n- **Module**: `example`\n- **Language